  "title": "Assistant Testing & Commissioning Engineer #HHW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist to prepare and review T&C procedures and checklists</li><li>T&C works associated with LRT electrical/signalling system</li><li>Perform and supervise testing and commissioning work as per approved procedures</li><li>Communicating effectively with the T&C manager, design engineers, site supervisors, project manager, and other internal stake holders.</li><li>Communicating effectively with various external stake holders e.g. other contractors (System Wide Contractors), Subcontractors</li><li>Assisting in troubleshooting and rectification of faults during T&C</li><li>Any other ad-hoc works assigned by project manager and commissioning manager</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: wendykhoo@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendy Khoo Hui Wen (R1761665)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p>",
